data.description: Prepare to be amazed by the unexpected spaciousness of 2315 Marston Lane! This isn't your average home - it's a great oasis tucked away on a picturesque tree-lined street in vibrant Flossmoor Park.  Step inside and discover a world of possibilities. The living room has tons of light, and a great fireplace feature wall.  There's a separate dining room that is a great casual gathering space more than it is formal.  2 full bedrooms and a full bath on this level, too.  Through the kitchen is the back addition, complete with its own HVAC system, which transforms into a lovely primary suite with a full bath, open closet, and direct access to the lush backyard oasis. Imagine sipping your morning coffee surrounded by garden beds and a cozy seating area. Upstairs are two more bedrooms and another full bath.  Descend into the finished basement and uncover even more potential. With ample storage, a laundry area, and newer carpeting.  And let's talk about location. Situated close to town, schools, and a convenient train ride to both the city and the University of Chicago, this home offers the perfect blend of suburban charm and urban convenience.
